text: Katalin Kisne Dancsa is a Hungarian water polo player. She competed for the Hungarian women's national water polo team in the 1994 World Aquatics Championships 2001 World Aquatics Championships, 1991 European Water polo Championships, and 2001 European Water polo Championships. == References == Category:Living people Category:Hungarian water polo players Category:1963 births
